theorem Topology.dense_iff_interior_closure_eq_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    Dense (A : Set X) ↔ interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    exact
      Topology.dense_implies_interior_closure_eq_univ (X := X) (A := A) hDense
  · intro hInt
    -- First, show that `closure A = univ`.
    have h_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) := by
      -- `interior_subset` gives `interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A`.
      have h : interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) :=
        interior_subset
      simpa [hInt] using h
    have h_closure_eq_univ : closure (A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
      apply Set.Subset.antisymm
      · exact Set.Subset_univ
      · exact h_subset
    -- Convert the equality into the `Dense` property.
    dsimp [Dense]
    simpa using h_closure_eq_univ

theorem Topology.closureInterior_eq_closure_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (hA : IsOpen (A : Set X)) :
    closure (interior (A : Set X)) = closure (A : Set X) := by
  simpa [hA.interior_eq]
